            </div>
            </article>
            <!-- 장르별 추천 영화 -->
            <article class="content-movie-genre" id="genre">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-video"></i>&nbsp;지금 D.NEMA에서 추천하는 영화를 살펴보세요!</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li class="best-movies bnt_open">
                        <div class="genre-img">
                            <video muted autoplay loop>
                                <source src="/static/video/random_action0.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                              </video>
                        </div>
                    <p class="genre-title">action</p>
                    <div class="bar"></div>
                    <div class="info action-info">
                        #드웨인존슨 X #제이슨스타뎀<br>
                        올 여름, 최고의 액션 빅 매치<br>
